plot: At Vicki's tense dinner party, Peggy and Alexis reach a boiling point, and Peggy ends her friendship with Alexis and the other women. Gretchen poses nude for a photo shoot for a charitable cause, while OC's newest housewife, Heather, has it all and isn't afraid to flaunt it. Meanwhile, Vicki and Tamra go on a trip to Catalina with their boyfriends that nearly ends before it begins when Tamra puts Brooks in an embarrassing situation.—Anonymous
